Release Notes for Version 3.10.6
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.10.6 is the seventh release in Errata Tool 3.10. It closes [28 bugs
and RFEs][buglist].

Major new features in this release include an improved user interface for
adding builds to an advisory and a new UI and API for managing users.

The new interface for adding builds displays a progress bar showing the
currently executing Brew query. This should be useful particularly when adding
many builds to an advisory, or when Brew's responses are slow.

